data.description: Seller will contribute towards buyer costs on this attractive home in desirable location featuring a GORGEOUS FREEFORM POOL, split bedroom plan, impact windows and city water and sewer.  So many desirable features that with a little updating this home will shine as the Gem in the neighborhood!  Covered entry leads  to living room and flows to kitchen with granite tops, newer appliances, breakfast bar, and is open to a family room with vaulted ceiling.     No carpet as all rooms have vinyl, tile, or laminate flooring.  Check out the HUGE 18 x 15 primary suite features a large shower and full bath and enjoys a convenient exit to the large pavered patio. Low maintenance vinyl fencing surrounds the backyard and pool.  Dimensional shingle roof was installed in 2017 and A/C in 2020..  TV wall mount in each bedroom.
